(626, 1, '2017-03-26 11:58:27', '2017-03-26 04:58:27', '[vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content" css=".vc_custom_1450363943036{background-color: #f1f6f9 !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" is_section="yes" section_skin="light" remove_margin_top="yes" remove_margin_bottom="yes" offset="vc_col-lg-6" el_class="match-height " animation_type="fadeIn"][vc_custom_heading text="Piano Tuning &amp; Restoration Services" font_container="tag:h1|text_align:left" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" skin="primary"][vc_column_text el_class="txt_color"]Artisan Piano Services provides a unique blend of old world craftsmanship and care with today’s technology and convenience while delivering unparalleled piano service.  We’ve built our reputation on the excellence of our artisans as well as the absolute quality of services we provide.\n\nWith our staff of highly trained technicians, we carry on the time-honored tradition of music, art and craftsmanship. Whether you are an accomplished professional, a budding artist, a teacher, or a family of beginners, our qualified piano technicians will create a memorable and worthwhile experience at each piano service.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="Peace of Mind Guarantee" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal"][vc_column_text el_class="txt_color"]We guarantee that our expert piano tuners will leave you completely satisfied with your piano tuning service, or we will make it right. Our promise to you that if you ever have any problems after we service your piano, call us and we’ll send one of our technicians out free of charge to address your concerns. You have our word. <strong>– Artisan Piano Services</strong>[/vc_column_text][vc_btn ti