(712, 1, '2017-03-26 22:07:00', '2017-03-26 15:07:00', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Full Service Packages" font_container="tag:h1|text_align:left" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Is your piano living up to it’s full potential? We can work with you to maximize the sound and performance of your piano.\n\nOur 3 full-service maintenance packages are designed to address the needs we have have found most common in pianos after years of playing. These packages are for those whose piano’s are in need of more than our standard tuning package.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="price_box"][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1490540807148{padding-top: 10px !important;padding-right: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;padding-left: 10px !important;background-color: #fbfbf5 !important;border-radius: 3px !important;}"]\n<div class="package_heading"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://artisanpianos.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/bronze2.fw_.png" alt="" /></div>\n<div>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Bronze Package</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">The Bronze Package is perfect for the average piano player. It will make a significant improvement in the way the piano sounds and plays – enhancing your enjoyment of the instrument.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3>Service Includes</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Tuning</li>\n 	<li>Preliminary Cleaning</li>\n 	<li>Minor Repairs</li>\n 	<li><span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" data-original-title="The process of adjusting the mechanical components of a piano to compensate for the wear, settling, and changes that have occurred over the years. This process is meant to help the piano play more evenly and consistently.">Regulation</span> of the Pedals</li>\n 	<li>Assessment of the Piano’s Condition</li>\n 	<li>1 hour of Touch Up Regulation and <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" data-original-title="Also called tone regulation, is the process of adjusting the tone of the piano so as to make it more pleasing to the ear. This process is done by softening or in some cases hardening the hammers to create a different color of tone.">Voicing</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>As with all of our services you get our Peace of Mind Guarantee!</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="price text-center" style="text-align: center;">$250</div>\n<div class="wrap-btn text-center"><a href="http://artisanpianos.com/schedule-online/"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://artisanpianos.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/bnt1.jpg" alt="" /></a></div>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1490540152188{padding-top: 10px !important;padding-right: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;padding-left: 10px !important;background-color: #fbfbf5 !important;border-radius: 3px !important;}"]\n<div class="package_heading"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://artisanpianos.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/silve-1.png" alt="" /></div>\n<div>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Silver Package</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">The Silver Package is a service designed for people who play their piano frequently, are more than beginners, and demand more from the piano. This service will make a substantial enhancement in the tone, and the way the piano plays and feels.</p>\n\n<h3>Service Includes</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Tuning</li>\n 	<li>Preliminary Cleaning</li>\n 	<li>Minor Repairs</li>\n 	<li><span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" data-original-title="The process of adjusting the mechanical components of a piano to compensate for the wear, settling, and changes that have occurred over the years. This process is meant to help the piano play more evenly and consistently.">Regulation</span> of the Pedals</li>\n 	<li>Assessment of the Pia