(737, 1, '2017-03-26 22:35:36', '2017-03-26 15:35:36', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=" Awards and Media" font_container="tag:h1|text_align:left"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Angie’s List</h2>\r\nAngie’s List is a fantastic resource for people to find qualified service professionals in any industry. Customers are able to choose service companies based on their reviews, performance, and overall rating. Angie’s List has also named us one of the Northwest’s top businesses as well as featured us in a nationwide article on instrument repair. Artisan Piano Services is honored to have received the Angie’s List Super Service Award multiple times for both of our locations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]<a href="http://www.angieslist.com/articles/musical-instrument-repairs-sing-these-mechanical-maestros.htm" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-356 size-full" src="http://artisanpianos.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/angieslist.jpg" alt="angieslist" width="235" height="156" data-id="356" /></a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]<img class="alignnone wp-image-1125" src="http://artisanpianos.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/angies-list-wall-of-fame.jpg" alt="angies-list-wall-of-fame" width="283" height="150" />[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]<img class="alignnone wp-image-1127 size-full" src="http://artisanpianos.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/angies-list-1.png" alt="angies-list" width="179" height="147" />\r\n<div class="video"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EkiatMWEVNI?rel=0" width="400" height="225" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe>\r\nIn the spring of 2016 we were featured in a news segment on a local ABC news affiliate in Portland, Oregon. It highlighted our piano restoration and rebuilding efforts, and was entitled: A labor of love: ‘Completely redoing a piano is kind of where my heart is’</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Awards and Media', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'awards-and-media', '', '', '2017-03-26 22:43:24', '2017-03-26 15:43:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/piano/?page_id=737', 0, 'page', '', 0),
