(741, 1, '2017-03-26 22:47:53', '2017-03-26 15:47:53', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Testimonials" font_container="tag:h1|text_align:left"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n<article id="post-443" class="post-443 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n<p class="first">Price was very reasonable, great service, and the piano that I was previously told was un-tunable, sounds fantastic.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Laurie G.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-442" class="post-442 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">I confidently recommend Artisan Pianos to all of my students for their piano tuning and repair needs.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Carol M.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-441" class="post-441 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">My piano now sounds like new again!  I would highly recommend this company to everyone.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Beverly R.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-440" class="post-440 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">Artisan Piano Services not only has great service, they have very professional and friendly staff and piano technicians.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Amy P.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-439" class="post-439 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">These folks are great! They communicate clearly, return your calls promptly, and always show up when they say they will.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Elaine L.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-438" class="post-438 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">We have had the technicians at Artisan Piano Services tune our piano several times and have been very pleased each time. The technicians are prompt, courteous and do excellent work. In addition to regular tuning, Artisan Piano Services also replaced the keys on our 112 year old piano and did a superb job. I highly recommend them!</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Lisa P.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-437" class="post-437 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">Our piano had some problems before and lasted for years until a friend recommended the technician from Artisan.  He came in and fixed the problem in just a few minutes!  I was amazed by his experience and professionalism.  They have been tuning our piano since. We are very happy about their service and courtesy.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">J. Linn</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-436" class="post-436 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">My experience with Artisan Piano Services was outstanding.  I got an appointment right away and the technician arrived on schedule.  He was extremely courteous, even taking his shoes off before stepping on my hardwood floors!  He did a wonderful job and was helpful in diagnosing potential future problems on my 60 year old piano that hadn’t been tuned in years.  He offered to come out and make adjustments for free if particular keys went out of tune again right away.  I’ll definitely continue to use Artisan Piano Services.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Susan G.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-435" class="post-435 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">I recently shipped my 1953 Steinway M to Portland from Spokane.  I was concerned about the condition since it had been in storage for 3 years. Artisan came out after it had settled in for about a month and tuned it beautifully.  It had gone almost 1/4 tone sharp! Gave it a good cleaning and examination and fortunately found it in good shape.  They were on time and did an excellent job. Look forward to next tuning and possible voicing.  Highly recommend this company.  Very happy with their work.</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Jim O.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article id="post-434" class="post-434 testimonials type-testimonials status-publish hentry">\r\n<div class="entry-content i first last">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="first">Fantastic, prompt service, willing to travel, and extremely reasonable rates! David was thorough and professional and the staff bent over backwards when I was worried about a buzzing sound that ended up disappearing on its own; they could have easily shrugged it off and let me deal with it on my own, but they went above and beyond to make sure I was satisfied. I highly recommend Artisan Piano Services!</p>\r\n<p class="testified r">Jon N.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Testimonials', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'testimonials', '', '', '2017-03-26 22:51:34', '2017-03-26 15:51:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/piano/?page_id=741', 0, 'page', '', 0),
